description:
Turbo is up for any trucking challenge, but waiting for pay from his last job means this hard driving, hard talking trucker is stuck 4300kms from home. Later, deep in the outback, tipper trucker Sharon faces a rocky road hauling a 50m road train packed full of gold ore. Meanwhile, Yogi is getting ready for one of the biggest and most stressful weeks of his career transporting huge agricultural machines.
